                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18401214-313-offence-1 t18401214-cd-60"></join>3rd of December</rs>, 6 brushes, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18401214-name-426" type="victimName">
